title: NBA Playoffs ft. Chandler Parsons & Amari Bailey Talks Iverson Classic and UCLA | WHAT’S BURNIN
itunes:title: NBA Playoffs ft. Chandler Parsons & Amari Bailey Talks Iverson Classic and UCLA | WHAT’S BURNIN
description:
In a jam-packed episode of WHAT'S BURNIN, Matt & Stak are joined by Chandler Parsons to recap the playoffs so far and look ahead at upcoming games. Plus, they talk with high school star Amari Bailey about playing with Bronny Jr. at the Sierra Canyon, the upcoming Iverson Classic & his college commitment to UCLA.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
